@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    Technical logs and error diagnostics

    This site may collect standard technical information when pages are requested or when an error occurs. This may include the requested URL, timestamp, browser user agent, referrer, IP address, and error details such as exception type and stack trace. I use this information to operate, debug, secure, and improve the site.

    I do not use this information for advertising, and I do not sell it.
</p>
